(v) ventilation systems, including fire and smoke dampers, fans 

and their controls; 

(vi) emergency shutdown of fuel supply; 

(vii) fire doors, including their controls; 

(viii) general emergency alarm systems; 

(ix) emergency escape breathing devices; 

(x) portable fire extinguishers, including spare charges; and 

(xi) 

fire-fighter's outfits. 

(3) The maintenance programme may be computer-based. 

